item.title: Contact Information
item.description: Laurence is based in the Centre for Research in Mathematics and Data Science at Western Sydney University. Name: Assoc. Prof. Laurence A. F. Park Position: Director of Academic Programs (Data Science) Address: School of Computer, Data and Mathematical Sciences, Western Sydney University, Locked Bag 1797, Penrith, New South Wales 2751, Australia Phone: +61 2 9685 9065 (Work) Room: EN.1.32 Parramatta Campus Email: lapark@scem.westernsydney.edu.au Photo courtesy of Rami Mukhtar.
